1. d4 d5 2. e4 dxe4 3. Nc3 Nf6 4. f3 exf3 5. Nxf3 g6 6. Bg5 {Not the main line, 
but in keeping with our repertoire and easy to play.} Bg7 7. Qd2 O-O 8. O-O-O 
{White has an easy attack with Bh6, maybe Bc4, h4 - h5 etc.} *

