1. d4 d5 2. e4 dxe4 3. Nc3 Nf6 4. f3 exf3 5. Nxf3 Bg4 6. h3 Bf5 7. g4 Bd7 8. g5 
{In the introduction I showed a quick blitz game I played where I opted for the 
immediate Ne5; the computers prefer g5 first.} Nh5 9. Ne5 Ng3 10. Qf3 {One good 
fork deserves another.} Nxh1 11. Qxf7# {Scott isn't the most ferocious 
opposition is he? Next!} *

